{"word":"G257 - ἅλων - hálōn - hal'-ohn - Floor","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἅλων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hálōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hal'-ohn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Floor</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"களம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"a ground - plot or threshing - floor"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably form the base of <a href=\"#/G1507 - εἱλίσσω - heilíssō - hi-lis'-so/1507\">G1507</a>; a threshing <i>floor</i> (as <i>rolled</i> hard), that is, (figuratively) the <i>grain</i> (and chaff, as just threshed): - floor.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}